<div class="extLoad" id="kathelyne">
  <div class="imgWrapper"><img src="//akvo.org/wp-content/themes/Akvo-responsive/images/staff/kathelyne240x135.png" title="Kathelyne van den Berg" Alt="Kathelyne van den Berg, Chief financial officer" /></div>
